          "range": "33311-33390",
          "rangeStart": 33311,
          "rangeEnd": 33390,
          "markText": "So we beat on, boats against the current, borne back ceaselessly into the past.\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1651586504,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2022-05-03 22:01:44",
          "chapterUid": 24,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=33311&rangeEnd=33390",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=33311&rangeEnd=33390"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "chapterTitle": "Before",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23636187_15_594-913",
          "range": "594-912",
          "rangeStart": 594,
          "rangeEnd": 912,
          "markText": "Then wear the gold hat, if that will move her;\nIf you can bounce high, bounce for her too,\nTill she cry \"Lover, gold-hatted, high-bouncing lover,\nI must have you! \"\n—THOMAS PARKE D'INVILLIERS\n",
          "colorStyle": 1,
