  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_5_786-825",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "786-825",
      "markText": "“每当你要批评别人，”他告诉我，“要记住，世上不是每个人都有你这么好的条件。”",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=786&rangeEnd=825",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=786&rangeEnd=825"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_3_13872-13917",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "13872-13917",
      "markText": "不随便评判别人，是因为事物的表象往往和本质不符，很多事情看起来是一回事，实际上又是一回事。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=13872&rangeEnd=13917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=13872&rangeEnd=13917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_5_1104-1123",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1104-1123",
      "markText": "不去评判别人就是对别人怀有无限的希望。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1104&rangeEnd=1123",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1104&rangeEnd=1123"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_7_1689-1736",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1689-1736",
      "markText": "花园里充满了笑语和欢声、毫不经意的寒暄和转身即忘的介绍，还有彼此不知姓名的女人之间热烈的攀谈。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1689&rangeEnd=1736",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1689&rangeEnd=1736"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_7_16186-16279",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16186-16279",
      "markText": "每当看见那些囊中羞涩的年轻职员在商店橱窗之前倘佯，捱到晚饭时间形影相吊地去餐厅填肚子，我知道他们也深有同感——我们这些薄暮中的年轻职员啊，正在虚度一生中最灿烂的年华、一夜中最美好的时辰。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16186&rangeEnd=16279",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16186&rangeEnd=16279"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_5_19146-19227",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "19146-19227",
      "markText": "他对着黑黝黝的海面，奇怪地伸出双手，而且尽管离他很远，我能看出来他正在发抖。我不由向海那边望去，但什么也没看到，只见远处有一点微茫的绿光，兴许是谁家码头上的电灯。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19146&rangeEnd=19227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19146&rangeEnd=19227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_6_13397-13487",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13397-13487",
      "markText": "……我站在他的床边，而他坐在被窝里，穿着内衣，手里捧着一本大相册。 “美女与野兽……寂寞……拉货的老马……布鲁克林大桥……”",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13397&rangeEnd=13487",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13397&rangeEnd=13487"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_5_1149-1199",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1149-1199",
      "markText": "但其实他想说的是，基本的道德观念并非与生俱来、人人皆有的东西。现在我仍然牢记这个道理，以免误会别人。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1149&rangeEnd=1199",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1149&rangeEnd=1199"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_5_1228-1309",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1228-1309",
      "markText": "如此自夸宽厚待人之后，必须承认的是，我的宽厚也有个限度。别人的行为或有磐石般靠得住的基础，或有烂泥般靠不住的理由，可是一旦过分到某种程度，我也就不管背后的原因了。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636187&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1228&rangeEnd=1309",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f4a32d007168a8dbf4a8846?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1228&rangeEnd=1309"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636187_8_17072-17161",
